ere is no smooth transition between high-energy and\nlow-energy Kasner regimes, the latter with realistic compactification.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Apr 2018 22:20:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 21 Apr 2018 18:06:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-09"}
