nary analysis suggests could be useful M-dwarf targets\nfor TESS. We also compared the criteria to selection via absolute magnitude and\na combination of both methods. We found that colour selection in combination\nwith an absolute magnitude limit provides the most effective way of selecting\nM-dwarfs en masse.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Apr 2018 02:42:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-20"}
