eter $Q$ of the outer disc of DDO 154 using the THINGS HI rotation curve\nand velocity dispersion map. 72% of the HI in our field has $Q\\leq 4$ and this\nincorporates 96% of the observed MS stars. Hence 28% of the HI in the field is\nlargely dormant.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Apr 2018 10:29:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-02"}
