, and 2) the method we used to calculate tidal phases.\nAnyone willing to reproduce our results or to apply our methodology to custom\ndatasets can use the public information system tQuakes that we developed for\nthis work.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Apr 2018 15:35:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 26 Nov 2018 16:40:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-31"}
